Condition.name: GET6isMCNCMHasImpactedItemCreatable
Condition.expression: (((u.role_name="Mfg Process Planner" and u.project_name!="") or (u.role_name="Mfg Process Engineer" and u.project_name!="") or (u.role_name="Mfg Change Control" and u.project_name!="") or (u.role_name="DBA" and u.project_name!="") or (u.role_name="Approver")) AND Condition::GET6isMCNImpactedItemCreatableForPrimary(p, u) )
Condition.description: User's current project should be owning project of MCN User's current role should be Mfg Process Engineer or Mfg Process Planner User's cannot Add/Cut the ItemRevision from Impacted item folder for MCN whose Disposition and Maturity State are not None and Elaborating.

Condition.name: GET6isMCNCMHasProblemItemCreatable
Condition.expression: (((u.role_name="Mfg Process Planner" and u.project_name!="") or (u.role_name="Mfg Process Engineer" and u.project_name!="") or (u.role_name="Mfg Change Control" and u.project_name!="") or (u.role_name="DBA" and u.project_name!="") or (u.role_name="Approver")) AND Condition::GET6isMCNProblemItemCreatableForPrimary(p, u) )
Condition.description: User's current project should be owning project of MCN User's current role should be Mfg Process Engineer or Mfg Process Planner User's cannot Add/Cut the ItemRevision from Problem Item folder for MCN whose Disposition and Maturity State are not None and Elaborating

Condition.name: GET6isMCNCMHasSolutionItemCreatable
Condition.expression: (((u.role_name="Mfg Process Planner" and u.project_name!="") or (u.role_name="Mfg Process Engineer" and u.project_name!="") or (u.role_name="Mfg Change Control" and u.project_name!="") or (u.role_name="DBA" and u.project_name!="") or (u.role_name="Approver")) AND Condition::GET6isMCNSolutionItemCreatableForPrimary (p, u) )
Condition.description: User's current project should be owning project of MCN. User's current role should be Mfg Process Engineer or Mfg Process Planner. User's cannot Add/Cut the ItemRevision from Solutions folder for MCN whose Disposition and Maturity State are not None and Elaborating.
